 ('1', '1', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-01-12 16:12:58', '2017-01-12 16:12:58', '24776682-9b14-4436-b619-1e1cc56a0686'),
 ('2', '2', 'en_us', 'Kent State Student Media', '<p>Kent State Student Media makes the connections you need. Whether you are a student searching for an authentic media experience, a community member wanting to share your story, or simply somebody seeking quality news, information and entertainment, we deliver for you across 34 outlets through print, digital and social media.  <br /></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Student Media Connects', NULL, '', 'Ten media partners.', NULL, NULL, '', '210945217', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>We are your direct access to more than 70,000 people. We connect you to our audience through award-winning digital, print, film and broadcast media.</p>', 'Advertise With Us', 'Our Media Partners', 'Take a 90-second tour of Kent State Student Media ', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Seven hundred students.', 'One mission.', '<p>We have been serving Kent State University and the Kent community for more than 80 years with independent student-produced media. We have the outlets you need to reach the target audience you want.</p>', '2017-01-12 16:12:59', '2017-06-28 04:00:27', 'f78f163d-6654-40b7-9f92-e347dd1a8a48'),
 ('3', '3', 'en_us', 'We just installed Craft!', '<p>Craft is the CMS that’s powering Kentstatestudentmedia.com. It’s beautiful, powerful, flexible, and easy-to-use, and it’s made by Pixel &amp; Tonic. We can’t wait to dive in and see what it’s capable of!</p><!--pagebreak--><p>This is even more captivating content, which you couldn’t see on the News index page because it was entered after a Page Break, and the News index template only likes to show the content on the first page.</p><p>Craft: a nice alternative to Word, if you’re making a website.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-01-12 16:12:59', '2017-01-12 16:12:59', 'dfa73501-ee0c-49a1-9e07-9d9311da2157'),
