 ('110', '161', 'en_us', 'Student Media Board ', '<p>The Student Media Board is a standing University committee. The members of the committee serve \"as the institutional publisher or de facto licensee and acts in all matters pertaining to those media that are written or broadcast primarily by students and financed primarily by university-sanctioned student fees.\"  The SMB reports to the vice president for student affairs and the dean of the College of Communication and Information.</p>\n<p>The SMB is primarily responsible for selecting student leaders, approving annual budgets and hearing any grievances that cannot be otherwise resolved. The SMB does not dictate or determine editorial content for Student Media partners and gives responsibility for day-to-day editorial operations to the selected student leaders. The SMB gives day-to-day business operation responsibility to the director of Student Media. </p>\n<p>The board is made up of students, staff and faculty across the university, as well as media professionals outside of KSU. Voting members include faculty members appointed by the faculty senate, faculty members appointed by the school of journalism and mass communication faculty advisory committee, the JMC director, the CSI director, USG appointees, a graduate senate appointee, JMC undergraduate students, a JMC graduate student and a media professional. All student leaders, student media advisors and the director of student media serve as non-voting members. </p>\n<p>Check out the guidelines, members and meeting minutes below.<br /></p>', NULL, NULL, '[]', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'We\'ll go farther together ', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-04-22 21:50:41', '2017-06-05 21:15:38', '4ab20dbb-c122-4519-826a-77a8f89c25d6'),
 ('113', '164', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[]', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-04-24 13:36:19', '2017-04-24 13:40:12', '41e02416-36c9-4f6d-90aa-59fee6d4f2ce'),
 ('114', '165', 'en_us', 'Lorie Bednar', '<p>Lorie Bednar joined Kent State’s School of Journalism and Mass Communication in 2015 as an administrative clerk in the Kent State Student Media office. She now shares her time between both offices. (Other information you want to add)</p>\n<p><b>Words to Live By:</b></p>\n<p>Be Where Your Feet Are – Anonymous</p>\n<p><b>Personal</b>:</p>\n<p>Lorie is a graduate of Kent State University and loves everything about her Alma mater. If you don’t find her on campus, chances are you may run into her downtown and throughout Kent, where she lives and enjoys spending time with her husband and three kids. Two of her greatest achievements are winning an Associated Press award for enterprise writing and being the illustrator of a book jacket.</p>\n<p><b>I can help you with:</b></p>\n<ul><li><p>KEYS!</p></li><li><p>Staff lists</p></li><li><p>Job offers</p></li><li><p>Travel</p></li><li>General questions</li></ul>', NULL, '', '[\"officeStaff\"]', 'Lorie', 'Bednar', 'Administrative Clerk', NULL, '330-672-3290', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-04-24 17:37:01', '2017-04-24 17:37:01', '5e0b009f-baba-4aef-b7db-adf004400e1c'),
 ('115', '166', 'en_us', 'Support Us', '<p>We like to think big. And sometimes our budget can\'t keep up. Your generous gift helps our students build on their big ideas. Your gift can be directed at a specific media partner or go directly to support Student Media in general.  Past support has helped us send students to cover election night 2016 in New York City, send other students to California to cover the NCAA basketball tournament, and has helped other students produce full-length feature films. No gift is too small. We\'ll put 100% of your donation to work immediately. </p>', NULL, NULL, '[]', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-04-24 17:57:47', '2017-06-13 18:26:02', '3f83ff12-8d53-4e79-a85f-e15d4731d040'),
