 ('286', '2', '1', '1', 'en_us', '28', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Kent State Student Media\",\"slug\":\"homepage\",\"postDate\":1484237579,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>Award-winning, nationally recognized and locally focused. Our independent, student-run media partners create content the campus and Kent community seek. Students learn practical skills through the professional learning opportunities available through Kent State Student Media. Advertising with Kent State Student Media is an excellent way to make sure you reach your audience.<\\/p>\",\"12\":\"This is our description\",\"13\":[\"64\",\"90\",\"88\"],\"16\":\"\",\"17\":\"\",\"25\":\"\",\"21\":\"Independent media connecting Kent State students and the Kent community\",\"22\":\"https:\\/\\/player.vimeo.com\\/video\\/210945217\"}}', '2017-05-10 20:43:12', '2017-05-10 20:43:12', '909f4dfa-9be8-42ec-ae9c-5cc80789fd9f'),
 ('287', '58', '9', '1', 'en_us', '14', '', '{\"typeId\":\"9\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"About Kent State Student Media\",\"slug\":\"about\",\"postDate\":1492560894,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>Kent State Student Media empowers students to be the best they can be. Students of any major and grade level are able to join us and gain a fun, practical experience that will provide transferable skills for any career they choose. We believe diversity is a strength, and we welcome all to join us! Our wide array of Media Partners means that every student can find their best fit. <br><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Our Mission:<em><\\/em><\\/strong><em><\\/em><strong><em><br><\\/em><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong><em>Student Media empowers students<\\/em><\\/strong> through practical, collaborative and professional learning opportunities within an independent, student-led and multi-platform media framework.<em><\\/em><em><\\/em><strong><em><br><\\/em><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong><em>Our students create valued sources<\\/em><\\/strong> of journalism, information, entertainment and advertising and develop meaningful connections with our core audiences.<em><\\/em><em><\\/em><strong><em><br><\\/em><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong><em>We encourage excellence, leadership and accountability<\\/em><\\/strong> as students become innovative, ethical and skilled media producers within a diverse and global society. <br><\\/p>\",\"11\":[\"166\"],\"13\":[\"88\"],\"47\":\"<p>You can help further our mission! Learn about the different ways you can support us. <br><\\/p>\",\"21\":\"Through the combined effort of students and faculty, our mission is to provide a professional learning foundation for all.\"}}', '2017-05-10 21:29:19', '2017-05-10 21:29:19', 'c9dcde7c-df55-4a12-913f-26c7d9f47969'),
 ('288', '161', '21', '1', 'en_us', '6', '', '{\"typeId\":\"21\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Student Media Board Members\",\"slug\":\"board-members\",\"postDate\":1494414895,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>The Student Media Board is made up of various stakeholders to ensure that Kent State Student Media is the best that it can be. Voting members include <span class=\\\"panel-inner-wrap clearfix\\\">faculty members appointed by the faculty senate<\\/span>, <span class=\\\"panel-inner-wrap clearfix\\\">faculty members appointed by the school of journalism and mass communication faculty advisory committee<\\/span>, the JMC director, the CSI director, USG appointees, a graduate senate appointee, JMC undergraduate students, a JMC graduate student and a media professional. All student leaders, student media advisors and the director of student media serve as non-voting members. <br><\\/p><p>Check out the guidelines, members and meeting minutes below.<br><\\/p>\",\"49\":[\"204\"],\"13\":[\"88\"],\"21\":\"The Team That Makes It Happen\"}}', '2017-05-10 21:41:05', '2017-05-10 21:41:05', '765c8fe9-ff27-42ac-ae73-3dd2a157d7ca'),
