 ('379', '45', '8', '235', 'en_us', '6', '', '{\"typeId\":\"8\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Kevin Dilley\",\"slug\":\"kevin-dilley\",\"postDate\":1489335420,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"20\":[\"23\"],\"1\":\"<p>Kevin serves Student Media by providing management of our business and advising operations. He also works with student leaders, the board, faculty and other key partners to set a strategic direction for Student Media and mentors and advises student leaders. &nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Words to Live By:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>If you want to go fast, go alone. If you want to go far, go together. &nbsp;~ origin unknown.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Personal:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>I\\u2019ve traveled to Siberia, Malaysia, Mexico and 46 of 50 states in the U.S. I love going places and meeting new people, but I always yearn to return home. For me, that\\u2019s in Hudson with my two children, mi media naranja (si, hablo espa\\u00f1ol), and Pancho, my very best friend because, well he\\u2019s a dog and I\\u2019m a man. I hold degrees in journalism and visual communication from the University of Missouri and Ohio University. I\\u2019ve worked as a reporter, writer, photojournalist, editor, designer, web designer, project manager, consultant, professor and adviser. I love what I do because I\\u2019m constantly inspired by my students who bring ideas, enthusiasm, opportunity and optimism to this place every day.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>I can help you with:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul><li><p>General questions<\\/p><\\/li><li><p>Strategic planning<\\/p><\\/li><li><p>Idea development<\\/p><\\/li><li><p>Budgets<\\/p><\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"4\":\"kdilley@kent.edu\",\"5\":[\"director\",\"nonVoting\",\"officeStaff\"],\"6\":\"Kevin \",\"19\":[\"171\"],\"8\":\"Director of Student Media\",\"7\":\"Dilley\",\"10\":\"330-672-4603\"}}', '2017-05-31 20:10:55', '2017-05-31 20:10:55', '420003ae-d0d0-4f10-b200-e0d4017ff60f'),
