 ('430', '58', '9', '235', 'en_us', '25', '', '{\"typeId\":\"9\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"The Who. The What. The Why. \",\"slug\":\"about\",\"postDate\":1492560894,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"55\":\"<p>Advertise with us!<\\/p>\",\"1\":\"<p>Kent State Student Media is made up of 10 distinct and independent Student Media partners who create unique content and distribute that across 34 different outlets on multiple platforms.&nbsp;<br><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Our mission-driven leadership begins here:<\\/strong><strong><em><br><\\/em><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong><em>Student Media empowers students<\\/em><\\/strong> through practical, collaborative and professional learning opportunities within an independent, student-led and multi-platform media framework.<strong><em><br><\\/em><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong><em>Our students create valued sources<\\/em><\\/strong> of journalism, information, entertainment and advertising and develop meaningful connections with our core audiences.<strong><em><br><\\/em><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong><em>We encourage excellence, leadership and accountability<\\/em><\\/strong> as students become innovative, ethical and skilled media producers within a diverse and global society. <br><\\/p>\",\"11\":[\"166\"],\"13\":[\"246\"],\"47\":\"<p>We often have larger ideas than our budget will support. Your generous gift will help our students build on their big ideas. Your gift can be directed at a specific media partner or go to support Student Media in general. &nbsp;<br><\\/p>\",\"21\":\"Through the combined effort of students and faculty, our mission is to provide a professional learning foundation for all.\"}}', '2017-06-02 20:14:34', '2017-06-02 20:14:34', '70244029-29d7-400e-8300-d46f6c211cfc'),
