 ('531', '166', '22', '235', 'en_us', '6', '', '{\"typeId\":\"22\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Your support makes a difference\",\"slug\":\"support-us\",\"postDate\":1493318469,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>We like to think big. And sometimes our budget can\'t keep up. Your generous gift helps our students build on their big ideas. Your gift can be directed at a specific media partner or go directly to support Student Media in general. &nbsp;Past support has helped us send students to cover election night 2016 in New York City and send other students to California to cover the NCAA basketball tournament. We have produced full-length feature films with your help. &nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"13\":[\"248\"],\"21\":\"\"}}', '2017-06-07 19:01:06', '2017-06-07 19:01:06', '9333b6cc-8aae-486d-bce1-0941df208aab'),
 ('532', '62', '13', '235', 'en_us', '18', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Contact Student Media\",\"slug\":\"contact\",\"postDate\":1489688145,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>We\'d love to hear from you, whether it\'s about getting involved with Student Media, reaching out about individual partners and their content, or for advertising opportunities.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul><li>For advertising contact us at <a href=\\\"mailto:ads@ksustudentmedia.com\\\">ads@ksustudentmedia.com<\\/a>, 330-672-6306, or drop by our office during business hours, Monday through Friday 8 a.m to 5 p.m. in 205 Franklin Hall on the Kent State University Kent campus.&nbsp;<\\/li><li>For general Student Media questions, reach out to Director of Student Media, Kevin Dilley, at <a href=\\\"mailto:kdilley@kent.edu\\\">kdilley@kent.edu<\\/a>  or 330-672-0887. You\'ll also find him in 205 Franklin Hall.&nbsp;<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"13\":[\"271\"],\"21\":\"How can we help?\"}}', '2017-06-07 19:04:12', '2017-06-07 19:04:12', '12e8b2c3-bdd3-45f5-852d-0552c750ffe2'),
 ('533', '62', '13', '235', 'en_us', '19', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Contact Student Media\",\"slug\":\"contact\",\"postDate\":1489688145,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>We\'d love to hear from you, whether it\'s about getting involved with Student Media, reaching out about individual partners and their content, or for advertising opportunities.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul><li>For advertising contact us at <a href=\\\"mailto:ads@ksustudentmedia.com\\\">ads@ksustudentmedia.com<\\/a>, 330-672-6306, or drop by our office during business hours, Monday through Friday 8 a.m to 5 p.m. in 205 Franklin Hall on the Kent State University Kent campus.&nbsp;<\\/li><li>For general Student Media questions, reach out to Director of Student Media, Kevin Dilley, at <a href=\\\"mailto:kdilley@kent.edu\\\">kdilley@kent.edu<\\/a>  or 330-672-0887. You\'ll also find him in 205 Franklin Hall.&nbsp;<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"13\":[\"271\"],\"21\":\"How can we help?\"}}', '2017-06-07 19:09:53', '2017-06-07 19:09:53', 'fa0dd7f4-6d17-4750-8a58-41be6d77098c'),
 ('534', '60', '11', '235', 'en_us', '21', '', '{\"typeId\":\"11\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Get Involved\",\"slug\":\"get-involved\",\"postDate\":1492711027,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>Student Media is open to any students, staff or faculty at Kent State. Start as early as your freshman year and get involved in any of dozens of positions across our 10 Student Media partners. Gain important experience that will set you apart from your fellow students. Come share your voice and gain practical experience to help launch your career. To get started, check out current openings below or contact Kevin Dilley, director of Student Media, at kdilley@kent.edu.<\\/p>\",\"51\":{\"231\":{\"type\":\"faqs\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"question\":\"How can I become a student media leader?\",\"answer\":\"<p>Leaders of each Student Media partner are selected by the Student Media Board in the fall and spring of each year for the following semester or semesters. To be considered, you must be must have at least a verified cumulative 2.25 Grade Point Average at the time of application and maintain a cumulative 2.25 GPA and be in good standing with the University during your term as leader. &nbsp;To be a compensated student leader, you must be enrolled in a minimum of eight credit hours as an undergraduate student and a minimum of six as a graduate student during their term. You&nbsp;do not need to be majors enrolled in the School of Journalism and Mass Communication. &nbsp;Candidates applying for leadership positions in the JMC-co-curricular units must have related experience to be considered an applicant.<\\/p>\"}},\"261\":{\"type\":\"faqs\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"question\":\"Can I get paid while working for Student Media?\",\"answer\":\"<p>Yes. Student Media offers hundreds of paid positions each semester across our 10 Student Media partners. Contact us for more information. <\\/p>\"}},\"262\":{\"type\":\"faqs\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"question\":\"Can I study abroad and still be involved in Student Media?\",\"answer\":\"<p>Yes. Student Media supports students who opt for a semester abroad. Sometimes this can fit into a media outlet\'s content plan for that semester. Also, studying abroad will not affect your ability to continue on a path to a leadership position, if you so choose. <\\/p>\"}},\"263\":{\"type\":\"faqs\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"question\":\"Who makes the hiring decisions for Student Media?\",\"answer\":\"<p>It depends on the position you are seeking:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul><li>Top leaders for each media partner are selected by the Student Media Board<\\/li><li>Staff members within each media partner are selected by the student leader in consultation with the adviser<\\/li><li>Staff members in the Student Media office are selected by the professional staff. <\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"264\":{\"type\":\"faqs\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"question\":\"How many hours can I work?\",\"answer\":\"<p>That depends on your position and the needs of your outlet. You should talk with your student leader and adviser about the specific needs of each position. If you are in a paid position, you cannot work more than 28 hours each week. &nbsp;<\\/p>\"}},\"265\":{\"type\":\"faqs\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"question\":\"If I don\'t see a position I like, can I still work in Student Media?\",\"answer\":\"<p>Probably, let\'s talk. &nbsp;Student Media is growing and changing as rapidly as the professional fields we strive to emulate. So, if a position doesn\'t exist (and it\'s generally within the wheelhouse of media and communications), let\'s talk and figure out how to make it happen.&nbsp;<\\/p>\"}},\"282\":{\"type\":\"faqs\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"question\":\"Can I earn academic credit for my work in Student Media?\",\"answer\":\"\"}},\"283\":{\"type\":\"faqs\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"question\":\"How long does my employment last once I\'m hired in Student Media?\",\"answer\":\"\"}},\"284\":{\"type\":\"faqs\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"question\":\"Do I have to reapply for a job in Student Media every semester?\",\"answer\":\"\"}},\"285\":{\"type\":\"faqs\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"question\":\"Can I work for more than one outlet at the same time during a semester?\",\"answer\":\"\"}},\"286\":{\"type\":\"faqs\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"question\":\"Can I volunteer at a Student Media publication?\",\"answer\":\"<p>Yes. Some jobs are paid, others are volunteer or on a contributor basis. Check with the student leader for each organization to see what opportunities exist at the moment for that media partner.&nbsp;<\\/p>\"}},\"287\":{\"type\":\"faqs\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"question\":\"Who has editorial control over content?\",\"answer\":\"\"}},\"288\":{\"type\":\"faqs\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"question\":\"Where can I listen to Black Squirrel Radio?\",\"answer\":\"\"}},\"289\":{\"type\":\"faqs\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"question\":\"On which channel is TV2 broadcast?\",\"answer\":\"\"}}},\"13\":[\"248\"],\"56\":{\"232\":{\"type\":\"employeeOpportunities\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"hiring\":\"A Magazine\",\"position\":\"Graphic Designer\",\"positionDescription\":\"description\",\"contactInformation\":\"Mary Smith\"}}},\"21\":\"Start your freshman year. Stay until you graduate. \"}}', '2017-06-07 19:15:55', '2017-06-07 19:15:55', '416a6772-537f-43d7-874b-8474cd43208d'),
 ('535', '2', '1', '235', 'en_us', '48', '', '{\"typeId\":\"1\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Kent State Student Media\",\"slug\":\"homepage\",\"postDate\":1495818871,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"61\":[\"58\"],\"55\":\"<p>We are your direct access to more than 70,000 people. We connect you to our audience through award-winning digital, print, film and broadcast media.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>We have been serving Kent State University and the Kent community for more than 80 years with independent student-produced media. We have the outlets you need to reach the target audience you want.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>We look forward to partnering with you and look forward to your success.<\\/p>\",\"62\":[\"61\"],\"63\":\"Advertise With Us\",\"1\":\"<p>Kent State Student Media makes the connections you need. Whether you are a student looking for media experience, a community member wanting to share your story, or an audience member after quality news, information and entertainment, we deliver for you across 34 outlets through print, digital and social media platforms. &nbsp;<br><\\/p>\",\"12\":\"Student Media Connects\",\"13\":[\"238\",\"240\",\"242\",\"243\",\"241\",\"244\"],\"17\":\"\",\"64\":\"Our Media Partners\",\"21\":\"Seven hundred students.       Ten partners. One mission. \",\"22\":\"https:\\/\\/player.vimeo.com\\/video\\/210945217\",\"65\":\"Take a 90-second tour of Kent State Student Media \"}}', '2017-06-07 19:19:25', '2017-06-07 19:19:25', '7eeee7b8-7f0a-49cc-b5ba-558c1a4a2761'),
 ('536', '166', '22', '235', 'en_us', '7', '', '{\"typeId\":\"22\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Your support makes a difference\",\"slug\":\"support-us\",\"postDate\":1493318469,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>We like to think big. And sometimes our budget can\'t keep up. Your generous gift helps our students build on their big ideas. Your gift can be directed at a specific media partner or go directly to support Student Media in general. &nbsp;Past support has helped us send students to cover election night 2016 in New York City, send other students to California to cover the NCAA basketball tournament, and has helped other students produce full-length feature films. No gift is too small. We\'ll put 100% of your donation to work immediately.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"13\":[\"248\"],\"21\":\"\"}}', '2017-06-07 19:53:17', '2017-06-07 19:53:17', '815edc8b-85d8-4652-998f-e16907c4d3c6'),
 ('537', '101', '4', '235', 'en_us', '11', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Student Media Advertising\",\"slug\":\"student-media-ad-sales\",\"postDate\":1492116120,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"31\":\"\",\"1\":\"<p>Our Student Media Advertising and Marketing team can help your campus department or local business reach the audience you are seeking. Our staff of account executives will work hand-in-hand to ensure your message is delivered effectively, efficiently and within your budget. Kent State Student Media has 10 different media partners and more than 30 outlets to reach your target market. We provide advertising, promotional item design and ordering, design services, video and audio production, and mobile DJ services. Contact our team today to get started.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"4\":\"ads@ksustudentmedia.com\",\"36\":\"1\",\"13\":[\"220\"],\"14\":\"\",\"68\":\"\",\"10\":\"330-672-6303\",\"29\":\"An innovative, energetic team focused on connecting with our community partners\",\"26\":\"\",\"21\":\"A multi-service, multim-platform solution\"}}', '2017-06-07 19:57:20', '2017-06-07 19:57:20', '1635e93e-078d-458b-b25d-e5988163284f'),
 ('538', '101', '4', '235', 'en_us', '12', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Student Media Advertising\",\"slug\":\"student-media-ad-sales\",\"postDate\":1492116120,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"31\":\"\",\"1\":\"<p>Our Student Media Advertising and Marketing team can help your campus department or local business reach the audience you are seeking. Our staff of account executives will work hand-in-hand to ensure your message is delivered effectively, efficiently and within your budget. Kent State Student Media has 10 different media partners and more than 30 outlets to reach your target market. We provide advertising, promotional item design and ordering, design services, video and audio production, and mobile DJ services. Contact our team today to get started.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"4\":\"ads@ksustudentmedia.com\",\"36\":\"1\",\"13\":[\"220\"],\"14\":\"\",\"68\":\"\",\"10\":\"330-672-6303\",\"29\":\"An innovative, energetic team focused on connecting with our community partners\",\"26\":\"\",\"21\":\"A multi-service, multim-platform solution\"}}', '2017-06-07 19:57:39', '2017-06-07 19:57:39', '969f6c77-1251-484d-b615-197c1bf4450c'),
 ('539', '24', '4', '235', 'en_us', '17', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Luna Negra\",\"slug\":\"luna-negra\",\"postDate\":1488484140,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"31\":[\"68\"],\"1\":\"<p>Luna Negra, though sometimes under different names, has been around since 1956. It began under the English department, where it found its footing within the campus\\u2019s cultural atmosphere. Since then, the publication has been a staple of the university, witnessing the path Kent State has taken through the decades. We have published works describing the culture of collegiate 1950s, the Kent State shootings, and 9\\/11; the literary pieces published by Luna Negra, written by the students themselves, have chronicled every major cultural and historical event of America. Since its inception, and still to today, Luna Negra is run by students and filled with student content. We strive to foster creative activity across campus and seek to be the keeper and encourager of the student body\\u2019s creative spirit.<\\/p>\",\"4\":\"lunanegramag@gmail.com\",\"36\":\"1\",\"13\":[\"90\"],\"14\":[\"53\"],\"68\":\"\",\"10\":\"\",\"29\":\"Kent State\\u2019s literary and arts journal publishing a blend of poetry, prose, photography and illustration. \",\"26\":{\"129\":{\"type\":\"socialMediaBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"socialName\":\"facebook\",\"address\":\"https:\\/\\/www.facebook.com\\/lunanegramag\\/\"}},\"130\":{\"type\":\"socialMediaBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"socialName\":\"instagram\",\"address\":\"https:\\/\\/www.instagram.com\\/lunanegramagazine\\/\"}},\"131\":{\"type\":\"socialMediaBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"socialName\":\"twitter\",\"address\":\"https:\\/\\/twitter.com\\/lunanegramag\"}},\"132\":{\"type\":\"socialMediaBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"socialName\":\"website\",\"address\":\"http:\\/\\/www.lunanegramag.com\\/\"}}},\"21\":\"Kent State\'s Literary and Arts Journal\"}}', '2