 ('603', '2', '1', '235', 'en_us', '54', '', '{\"typeId\":\"1\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Kent State Student Media\",\"slug\":\"homepage\",\"postDate\":1495818871,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"61\":[\"58\"],\"55\":\"<p>We are your direct access to more than 70,000 people. We connect you to our audience through award-winning digital, print, film and broadcast media.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>We have been serving Kent State University and the Kent community for more than 80 years with independent student-produced media. We have the outlets you need to reach the target audience you want.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>We look forward to partnering with you and look forward to your success.<\\/p>\",\"62\":[\"61\"],\"63\":\"Advertise With Us\",\"1\":\"<p>Kent State Student Media makes the connections you need. Whether you are a student searching for an authentic media experience, a community member wanting to share your story, or simply somebody seeking quality news, information and entertainment, we deliver for you across 34 outlets through print, digital and social media. &nbsp;<br><\\/p>\",\"12\":\"Student Media Connects\",\"13\":[\"240\",\"242\",\"243\",\"241\",\"244\",\"238\"],\"17\":\"\",\"64\":\"Our Media Partners\",\"21\":\"Ten media partners. Seven hundred students. One mission. \",\"22\":\"https:\\/\\/player.vimeo.com\\/video\\/210945217\",\"65\":\"Take a 90-second tour of Kent State Student Media \"}}', '2017-06-15 19:33:03', '2017-06-15 19:33:03', 'e46db82d-5fcc-4a84-b8a1-c299ebd59ca2'),
 ('604', '58', '9', '235', 'en_us', '38', '', '{\"typeId\":\"9\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"About us\",\"slug\":\"about\",\"postDate\":1492560894,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>For more than 90 years, students at Kent State University have been finding ways to tell stories and disseminate vital and compelling information.\\r\\n  <\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Even before formal journalism education classes had been established, students were chasing leads and documenting the events shaping our history, sharing their work in the Normal High School News and The Chestnut Burr in 1914, The Kentonian in 1915 and eventually the first issue of The Kent Stater on July 29, 1926.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>We now are more than 700 students working with 10 distinct and independent Student Media partners who create unique content distributed across 34 different outlets on multiple platforms. Our students are supported in their efforts by a strong fabric of faculty advisers, professional staff, university support and, of course, financial support from the students of Kent State University.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>And while the methods have varied since those early publications, our core philosophy has remained constant: empower students to create valued sources and encourage excellence.\\r\\n  <\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Won\\u2019t you join us and continue the story?<\\/p>\\r\\n<hr>\\r\\n<p><strong>Our mission-driven leadership begins here:<\\/strong><strong><em><br><\\/em><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>STUDENT MEDIA EMPOWERS STUDENTS<\\/strong> through practical, collaborative and professional learning opportunities within an independent, student-led and multi-platform media framework.<br><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>OUR STUDENTS CREATE <\\/strong>valued sources of journalism, information, entertainment and advertising and develop meaningful connections with our core audiences.<br><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>WE ENCOURAGE EXCELLENCE<\\/strong>, leadership and accountability as students become innovative, ethical and skilled media producers within a diverse and global society. <br><\\/p>\",\"11\":[\"166\"],\"13\":[\"246\"],\"71\":\"\",\"70\":\"\",\"47\":\"<p>We like to think big. And sometimes our budget can\'t keep up. Your generous gift helps our students build on their big ideas. Your gift can be directed at a specific media partner or go directly to support Student Media in general. &nbsp;<br><\\/p>\",\"21\":\"Through the combined effort of students and faculty, our mission is to provide a professional learning foundation for all.\"}}', '2017-06-15 19:38:17', '2017-06-15 19:38:17', 'b6214831-2292-4350-a901-3d5a7be22796'),
 ('605', '58', '9', '235', 'en_us', '39', '', '{\"typeId\":\"9\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"About us\",\"slug\":\"about\",\"postDate\":1492560894,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>For more than 90 years, students at Kent State University have been finding ways to tell stories and disseminate vital and compelling information.\\r\\n  <\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Even before formal journalism education classes had been established, students were chasing leads and documenting the events shaping our history, sharing their work in the Normal High School News and The Chestnut Burr in 1914, The Kentonian in 1915 and eventually the first issue of The Kent Stater on July 29, 1926.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>We now are more than 700 students working with 10 distinct and independent Student Media partners who create unique content distributed across 34 different outlets on multiple platforms. Our students are supported in their efforts by a strong fabric of faculty advisers, professional staff, university support and, of course, financial support from the students of Kent State University.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>And while the methods have varied since those early publications, our core philosophy has remained constant: empower students to create valued sources and encourage excellence.\\r\\n  <\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Won\\u2019t you join us and continue the story?<\\/p>\\r\\n<hr>\\r\\n<p><strong>Our mission-driven leadership begins here:<\\/strong><strong><em><br><\\/em><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>STUDENT MEDIA EMPOWERS STUDENTS<\\/strong> through practical, collaborative and professional learning opportunities within an independent, student-led and multi-platform media framework.<br><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>OUR STUDENTS CREATE <\\/strong>valued sources of journalism, information, entertainment and advertising and develop meaningful connections with our core audiences.<br><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>WE ENCOURAGE EXCELLENCE<\\/strong>, leadership and accountability as students become innovative, ethical and skilled media producers within a diverse and global society. <br><\\/p>\",\"11\":[\"166\"],\"13\":[\"246\"],\"71\":\"Members of the fall 2016 Burr staff pose for a picture. The Burr was recognized as the best student magazine in the country by the Society of Professional Journalists.\",\"70\":[\"311\"],\"47\":\"<p>We like to think big. And sometimes our budget can\'t keep up. Your generous gift helps our students build on their big ideas. Your gift can be directed at a specific media partner or go directly to support Student Media in general. &nbsp;<br><\\/p>\",\"21\":\"Through the combined effort of students and faculty, our mission is to provide a professional learning foundation for all.\"}}', '2017-06-15 20:48:34', '2017-06-15 20:48:34', '4a55d139-786d-421d-9cbe-1531c8e0d4bc'),
