 ('19', '112', 'en_us', 'Inserts & Post-its', '[{\"col3\":\"Single-Page Insert\",\"col1\":\"$450\",\"col2\":\"\"},{\"col3\":\"Multi-Page Insert\",\"col1\":\"$500\",\"col2\":\"\"},{\"col3\":\"3\\\"x3\\\" or 4\\\"x5\\\" Post-it\",\"col1\":\"$600\",\"col2\":\"\"}]', 'Post-Its must be printed in a fan-fold and boxed. The unwind direction must be #1 or #3. Insert/Post-it sample must be submitted to Kent State Student Media for approval. Inserts/Post-its must be printed by the client and shipped directly to the printer at least one week prior to insertion. Inserts and Post-Its are within every copy of The Kent Stater. Advertisers should print and ship 6,750 total. Kent State Student Media can arrange the printing of the Post-Its for advertisers for an additional $75. Please ship directly to: Midwest Offset 629 Wabash Avenue NW New Philadelphia, Ohio 44663 800-837-8666', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-04-14 22:37:18', '2017-04-14 22:37:18', 'a8f3ab3e-ef07-4661-b92d-c90cc3034378'),
